mtd: s3c2410: Do not initialise statics to 0 or NULL

Fixes the following checkpatch errors:
ERROR: do not initialise statics to 0 or NULL
+static int hardware_ecc = 0;

ERROR: do not initialise statics to 0 or NULL
+static const int clock_stop = 0;

